<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108876.figures14-17>
    dc:description "Figures 14 - 17. Loxocera (Loxocera) lonsdalei sp. nov., male genitalia 14 sternite 8 to genitalia, caudal 15 same, lateral 16 pregonite and phallus, ventral 17 hypandrium and associated structures, ventral. Abbreviations: ce = cercus, ea = ejaculatory apodeme, ep = epandrium, ha = hypandrial arm, hb = hypandrial bridge, hl = hypandrial lobe, pg = pregonite, s 8 = sternite 8, ph = phallus, pt = phallotrema. Scale bars: 0.25 mm (14, 15, 17); 0.1 mm (16)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/950424" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

